&lt;li&gt;Review test code and provide high-quality, actionable feedback&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Drive improvements in testing processes, tools, and overall quality practices&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Estimate effort at the feature level and support delivery planning&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Deploy to and maintain test environments&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Participate in and occasionally lead production incident response&lt;/li&gt;
